Package: sigminerUtils
Title: Utilities for Running Signature Analysis using Sigminer
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sam", "El-Kamand", , "selkamand@ccia.org.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2270-8088"))
Description: A collection of utilities for running signature analysis with sigminer. 
    Results are stored in a sqlite database and indexed for downstream analysis.
